      </p>
      <div class="wizard-steps-grid">
        <div class="wizard-step">
          <div class="wizard-step-title">1. Identity</div>
          <div class="wizard-step-desc">Name and tagline</div>
        </div>
        <div class="wizard-step">
          <div class="wizard-step-title">2. Personality</div>
          <div class="wizard-step-desc">Traits and style</div>
        </div>
        <div class="wizard-step">
          <div class="wizard-step-title">3. Voice</div>
          <div class="wizard-step-desc">Pick and preview</div>
        </div>
        <div class="wizard-step">
          <div class="wizard-step-title">4. Knowledge</div>
          <div class="wizard-step-desc">Expertise areas</div>
        </div>
        <div class="wizard-step">
          <div class="wizard-step-title">5. Behaviors</div>
          <div class="wizard-step-desc">Greetings</div>
        </div>
        <div class="wizard-step">
          <div class="wizard-step-title">6. Review</div>
          <div class="wizard-step-desc">Submit</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-content">
      <div class="step-header">
        <div class="step-icon">3</div>
        <h3>Choose a Voice</h3>
      </div>
      <p>
        Browse our library of Cartesia voices. Click any voice to hear a preview with your greeting text. 
        Each voice has different characteristics—warm, professional, energetic, calm.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="step-content">
      <div class="step-header">
        <div class="step-icon step-icon-success">4</div>
        <h3>Publish</h3>
      </div>
      <p>
        The wizard validates your persona automatically. Submit for review and your persona 
        will be available within a few days.
      </p>
      <a href="/personas/create/" class="btn btn-primary">Create Persona →</a>
